**Overall Meaning:**

"Always being the witness, I am only the auspicious (Shiva). This is the wisdom, which is said to be meditation here, by the best among sages." 

**In simpler terms:**

The true self is the eternal witness, pure and auspicious. This understanding, which is the essence of meditation, is the wisdom of the greatest sages. 
